Smart firewall alias manager for OPNsense.

Monitors DNS hostnames and URL feeds, then atomically syncs resolved
IPs into pf tables via pfctl -T replace. No filter reload, no dropped
connections.

Features:
- DNS watchers with configurable intervals (10s-3600s)
- URL feed watchers for threat feeds and cloud provider IP ranges
- Atomic pf table updates without filter reload
- Change detection with before/after logging
- Failure alerting with consecutive error tracking
- Live status dashboard with per-watcher diagnostics
- Manual "Refresh Now" button for debugging
- IPv4 + IPv6 dual-stack support

